		<div class="pae-icon"><svg class="icon icon-merchandise"><use xlink:href="#icon-merchandise"></use></svg></div>
		<h4 class="pae-title uppercase">Buy Merch</h4>
		<p class="pae-des">Support our site and tell people how you really feel.</p>
